{"tid":2060341,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個識網友既經歷","createTime":"2020-06-11T14:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T16:36:38.000Z","uid":6783,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac3a4fa6126fdc9013e875eb6cb79bfd5aec907","tid":2060341,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 個陣係外國生活, 唔想一個人去旅行, 於是係高登開左個po, 好好彩咁識到個絲打,  大家仲好好傾, 最後都一齊去左冰島1個禮拜.<br />\n<br />\n旅行完，大家都keep住有contact, 中間又有約出嚟食飯，但係偏偏自己嗰陣鐘意左第二個.<br />\n<br />\n直到之後既聖誕節, 佢寫俾我張卡俾我，而入面既內容好感動, 同埋係佢親手整。到依家我都有keep住，每次唔開心, 我都會拎返出黎睇。<br />\n<br />\n可惜最後冇一齊到."},{"pid":"df63888c32b2946e88686fbc1b309936d3798b29","tid":2060341,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"想同絲打創造個經歷分享 <br />\n請pm我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a509e12b6aa3bbf43cccb3a151acb23096c8532a","tid":2060341,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df63888c32b2946e88686fbc1b309936d3798b29","tid":2060341,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"想同絲打創造個經歷分享 <br />\n請pm我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"我巴打"},{"pid":"90b3af4e93ad90af82b5985d7230cb240e49bf2e","tid":2060341,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a509e12b6aa3bbf43cccb3a151acb23096c8532a","tid":2060341,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df63888c32b2946e88686fbc1b309936d3798b29","tid":2060341,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"想同絲打創造個經歷分享 <br />\n請pm我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"我巴打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！"},{"pid":"e601e03561a58c7b5683b0ad90a28af7bcd2f18a","tid":2060341,"uid":228688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor